snippet.title: Yuuhime - Sea Of Sorrow (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
The stage is set for the hunter to bare her sharp claws and fangs and put a stop to the wails.
The puppet master tugs on his strings... Manipulating and weaving his nightmare into reality.
On the grand stage of life, there are no triumphant warriors.
In the shadows behind the scenes, there are no free spirits.
When will this never-ending drama come to an end?

#Dislyte #SeaOfSorrow #Yuuhime #Izanami #Yamato #Izanagi
#シンネオ #디스라이트 #众神派对
